436
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:22,600
And knowing the difference
is called science.

437
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:24,800
The second question
you could ask is:

438
00:23:24,880 --> 00:23:27,320
"Has this been held up
to scrutiny by experts?"

439
00:23:27,400 --> 00:23:29,760
"And if so,
what did those experts say?"

440
00:23:30,160 --> 00:23:33,720
Because it's not uncommon
